Class InFlightContainer

    • uk.ac.cam.cl.juliet.master.clustermanagement.distribution.InFlightContainer

  • public class InFlightContainer
extends java.lang.Object
    This class holds the record of the container that was sent to the cluster. This class is never sent but resides in the Client whilst it waits on a response.
